<lb n="0447c20"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0447c21"/><head type="no">No. 178</head>
<lb n="0447c22"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0447008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛說）＋前【三】【聖】</note><note n="0447008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（佛說）＋前【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0447008"><lem>前</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">佛說前</rdg></app>世三轉經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0447c23"/>
<lb n="0447c24"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0447009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔西晉…譯〕－【聖】</note><app n="0447009" word-count="7"><lem>西晉沙門<note n="0447010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（釋）＋法炬【三】</note><note n="0447010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（釋）＋法炬【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0447010"><lem>法炬</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">釋法炬</rdg></app><note n="0447011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（初）＋譯【三】</note><note n="0447011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（初）＋譯【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0447011"><lem>譯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">初譯</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0447c25"/><div1 type="jing"><p>聞如是。一時佛遊於舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。
<lb n="0447c26"/>與大比丘眾五百人。皆阿羅漢<note n="0447012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔也〕－【聖】</note><app n="0447012"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。一切大
<lb n="0447c27"/>聖皆其上尊。悉知他人心所念。獨阿難未也。
<lb n="0447c28"/>爾時佛出精舍坐於虛空。為無<note n="0447013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">央＝鞅【聖】＊</note><app n="0447013"><lem>央</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">鞅</rdg></app>數百千眾
<lb n="0447c29"/>會圍繞。而為說法。及七萬<note n="0447014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">菩薩＋（俱）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0447014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">菩薩＋（俱）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0447014"><lem>菩薩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">菩薩俱</rdg></app>。皆得諸總
<pb ed="T" id="T03.0178.0448a" n="0448a"/>
<lb n="0448a01"/>持。彼時佛面色光明勝常時。光明從面出往
<lb n="0448a02"/>照遍諸世界。時佛便笑。五色光從<note n="0448001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">口＋（中）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">口＋（中）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448001"><lem>口</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">口中</rdg></app>出。上
<lb n="0448a03"/>至梵天。諸佛天中天授諸弟子決時。光往照
<lb n="0448a04"/>四天王。<note n="0448002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">光還照＝還繞【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">光還照＝還繞【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448002"><lem>光還照</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">還繞</rdg></app>佛三匝從足心入。諸佛天
<lb n="0448a05"/>中天授辟支佛道決時。光從口<note n="0448003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔中〕－【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔中〕－【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448003"><lem>中</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>出。往照
<lb n="0448a06"/>波羅尼蜜天。還繞佛三匝從<note n="0448004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">臍＋（中）【三】</note><note n="0448004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">臍＋（中）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0448004"><lem>臍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">臍中</rdg></app>入。諸佛天中
<lb n="0448a07"/>天授佛道決時。光往照梵天。還繞佛三匝
<lb n="0448a08"/>從頂入。是時地神皆同時舉聲。如是佛<note n="0448005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＝現【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見＝現【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448005"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">現</rdg></app>
<lb n="0448a09"/>三事。若過去當來今現在說種種決。虛空神
<lb n="0448a10"/>天四天王忉利天上至梵天。皆舉作聲。如是
<lb n="0448a11"/>說三事<note n="0448006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（說）＋種【三】</note><note n="0448006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（說）＋種【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0448006"><lem>種</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">說種</rdg></app>種決。過去當來今現在。<note n="0448007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（是）＋為【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（是）＋為【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448007"><lem>為</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">是為</rdg></app>授弟
<lb n="0448a12"/>子地決。為授辟支佛地決。為授佛地決。時
<lb n="0448a13"/>梵天皆來下。上至三十三天人皆來下。爾時
<lb n="0448a14"/>無央數百千人。會<note n="0448008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（皆）＋比丘【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（皆）＋比丘【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448008"><lem>比丘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">皆比丘</rdg></app>比丘尼優婆塞優婆
<lb n="0448a15"/>夷。賢者阿難。時知七法事。何等為七。一者
<lb n="0448a16"/><note n="0448009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（知義…身事）二十三字＝知法二者知時三者知義四者知節五者知己身六者知眾會事【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（知義…身事）二十三字＝知法二者知時三者知義四者知節五者知己身六者知眾會事【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448009" word-count="23"><lem>知義。二者解法。三者曉時。四者了節。五
<lb n="0448a17"/>者明眾。六者知身事</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">知法二者知時三者知義四者知節五者知己身六者知眾會事</rdg></app>。七者知他人事。賢者
<lb n="0448a18"/>阿難從座起。整衣<note n="0448010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">被＝服【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">被＝服【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448010"><lem>被</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">服</rdg></app>長跪叉手。以偈讚佛
<lb n="0448a19"/>言</p>
<lb n="0448a20"/><lg><l><note n="0448011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得＝德【聖】</note><app n="0448011"><lem>得</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">德</rdg></app>清淨智眼明好</l><l>尊根寂定度無極</l>
<lb n="0448a21"/><l>光明<note n="0448012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遠照＝照遠【三】</note><note n="0448012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遠照＝照遠【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0448012"><lem>遠照</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">照遠</rdg></app>而金色</l><l>神照誰<note n="0448013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得＝德【三】</note><note n="0448013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得＝德【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0448013"><lem>得</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">德</rdg></app>願說之</l>
<lb n="0448a22"/><l>誰今發意於佛道</l><l>誰坐樹下降伏魔</l>
<lb n="0448a23"/><l>誰<note n="0448014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">今＝受【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">今＝受【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448014"><lem>今</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">受</rdg></app>取佛上道利</l><l>月<note n="0448015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">面＝而【聖】</note><app n="0448015"><lem>面</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">而</rdg></app>願說何故笑</l>
<lb n="0448a24"/><l>若佛世尊笑之時</l><l>面出光笑勝於人</l>
<lb n="0448a25"/><l>應時百千人民會</l><l>今佛以緣當<note n="0448016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">說之＝道說【聖】</note><app n="0448016"><lem>說之</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">道說</rdg></app></l></lg>
<lb n="0448a26"/><p>阿難問佛。<note n="0448017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惟＝唯【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惟＝唯【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448017"><lem>惟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">唯</rdg></app>天中<note n="0448018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天＋（人）【聖】</note><app n="0448018"><lem>天</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">天人</rdg></app>。諸有婬怒癡者。以
<lb n="0448a27"/>色聲香味細滑法故笑。天中天<note n="0448019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（已）＋斷【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（已）＋斷【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448019"><lem>斷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">已斷</rdg></app>婬怒癡。用
<lb n="0448a28"/>何故笑。天中天。不<note n="0448020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝用【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是＝用【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448020"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">用</rdg></app>舍利弗所問。亦不是
<lb n="0448a29"/>摩訶目犍連摩訶迦葉優為迦葉迦翼迦葉那
<pb ed="T" id="T03.0178.0448b" n="0448b"/>
<lb n="0448b01"/>翼迦葉<note n="0448021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（葉）＋施【三】</note><note n="0448021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（葉）＋施【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0448021"><lem>施</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">葉施</rdg></app>羅比利迦私所問。諸佛天中天。有
<lb n="0448b02"/>六法不共。何等為六。一者諸佛天中天知過
<lb n="0448b03"/>去無所罣礙慧。二者<note n="0448022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔諸佛天中天〕－【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔諸佛天中天〕－【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448022"><lem>諸佛天中天</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。有當來
<lb n="0448b04"/>無所罣礙慧。三者諸佛天中天。今現在亦有
<lb n="0448b05"/>無所罣礙慧。四者諸佛天中天。身所行智慧。
<lb n="0448b06"/>五者諸佛天中天。口所說智慧。六者諸佛天
<lb n="0448b07"/>中天心<note n="0448023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（所）＋念【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（所）＋念【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448023"><lem>念</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">所念</rdg></app>智慧。是為六。諸佛天中天<note n="0448024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無＝非【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無＝非【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448024"><lem>無</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">非</rdg></app>有
<lb n="0448b08"/>不見聞<note n="0448025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸＝願【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸＝願【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448025"><lem>諸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">願</rdg></app>佛說<note n="0448026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛〕－【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛〕－【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448026"><lem>佛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>道慧。佛告阿難。<note n="0448027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">過＋（去）【三】</note><note n="0448027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">過＋（去）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0448027"><lem>過</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">過去</rdg></app>世
<lb n="0448b09"/>時有國名優波羅越。其國富樂熾盛五穀豐
<lb n="0448b10"/>熟。人民安隱眾多不可<note n="0448028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔得〕－【三】，＝復【聖】</note><note n="0448028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔得〕－【宋】【元】【明】，＝復【聖】</note><app n="0448028"><lem>得</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">復</rdg></app>計。<note n="0448029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛語〕－【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛語〕－【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448029"><lem>佛語</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>阿難。
<lb n="0448b11"/>爾時優波羅越國中。有王名波羅先。於諸國
<lb n="0448b12"/>中獨尊。所施行教敕使人。<note n="0448030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（以）＋正法【三】，＝以法【聖】</note><note n="0448030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（以）＋正法【宋】【元】【明】，＝以法【聖】</note><app n="0448030"><lem>正法</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">以正法</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">以法</rdg></app>治國鞭杖不
<lb n="0448b13"/>行。爾時人<note n="0448031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">民＝命【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">民＝命【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448031"><lem>民</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">命</rdg></app>長壽二萬歲。時其王命過。其
<lb n="0448b14"/>國中有一婬&CB00105;<note n="0448032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">女＋（人名）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">女＋（人名）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448032"><lem>女</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">女人名</rdg></app>。為上色面貌端正姝好。
<lb n="0448b15"/>其女人<note n="0448033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（行）＋往【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（行）＋往【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448033"><lem>往</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">行往</rdg></app>至他人舍。其主人<note n="0448034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生男＝適生男子【三】，這生子男【聖】</note><note n="0448034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">生男＝適生男子【宋】【元】【明】，＝這生子男【聖】</note><app n="0448034"><lem>生男</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">適生男子</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">這生子男</rdg></app>。便以手
<lb n="0448b16"/>牽子臂。婬<note n="0448035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">女＋（人）【三】【聖】＊</note><note n="0448035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">女＋（人）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】＊</note><app n="0448035"><lem>女</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">女人</rdg></app>便問<note n="0448036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＋（言）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之＋（言）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448036"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">之言</rdg></app>。牽<note n="0448037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">兒＝子【三】【聖】＊</note><note n="0448037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">兒＝子【宋】【元】【明】【聖】＊</note><app n="0448037"><lem>兒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">子</rdg></app>欲作何等。<note n="0448038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（兒母）＋報【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（兒母）＋報【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448038"><lem>報</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">兒母報</rdg></app>
<lb n="0448b17"/>言。我飢餓欲噉之。<note n="0448039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（又）＋問【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（又）＋問【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448039"><lem>問</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">又問</rdg></app>言<note n="0448040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（寧）＋無【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（寧）＋無【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448040"><lem>無</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">寧無</rdg></app>有飯可食之耶。
<lb n="0448b18"/>報言。無有也。婬女人<note n="0448041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔報〕－【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔報〕－【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448041"><lem>報</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>言。且待<note n="0448042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">須＝頃【三】＊</note><note n="0448042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">須＝頃【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0448042"><lem>須</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">頃</rdg></app>我為
<lb n="0448b19"/>汝持食來。<note n="0448043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">答曰＝報言【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">答曰＝報言【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448043"><lem>答曰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">報言</rdg></app>。卿未出門頃我當餓死。<note n="0448044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">那＝耶【三】</note><note n="0448044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">那＝耶【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0448044"><lem>那</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">耶</rdg></app>
<lb n="0448b20"/><note n="0448045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（豈）＋能【聖】</note><app n="0448045"><lem>能</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">豈能</rdg></app>須卿持<note n="0448046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飯＝食【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飯＝食【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448046"><lem>飯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">食</rdg></app>來耶。婬女人念言。若我持兒
<lb n="0448b21"/>去其母便當餓死。若置去者便當取<anchor id="fxT03p0448b01"/>兒。噉
<lb n="0448b22"/>之。將當奈何令母子各得安隱。婬女人即取
<lb n="0448b23"/>利刀。自割兩乳與之。其母便食之。婬女人
<lb n="0448b24"/>問言。卿為飽未。報言。已飽矣婬女人兩乳
<lb n="0448b25"/>血出流離。便還其家。時有一男子至其婬女
<lb n="0448b26"/>人舍。欲與共作非法。<note n="0448047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見之便＝是人便念【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見之便＝是人便念【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448047"><lem>見之便</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">是人便念</rdg></app>言。誰取此上
<lb n="0448b27"/>色女乳割如是耶。便有<note n="0448048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悲＋（哀之）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悲＋（哀之）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448048"><lem>悲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">悲哀之</rdg></app>意以姊弟心<note n="0448049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">侍＝待【三】</note><note n="0448049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">侍＝待【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0448049"><lem>侍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">待</rdg></app>
<lb n="0448b28"/>之。不復起<note n="0448050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欲心＝婬意【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欲心＝婬意【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448050"><lem>欲心</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">婬意</rdg></app>。男子即問言。姊誰取卿如
<lb n="0448b29"/>是耶。報言。無有<note n="0448051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嬈＝取【聖】</note><app n="0448051"><lem>嬈</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">取</rdg></app>我<note n="0448052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（如是）＋者【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（如是）＋者【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448052"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">如是者</rdg></app>也。我自至他舍。其
<pb ed="T" id="T03.0178.0448c" n="0448c"/>
<lb n="0448c01"/>主人<note n="0448053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">適＝這【聖】＊</note><app n="0448053"><lem>適</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">這</rdg></app>產生便牽其子。我問言。欲作何等。
<lb n="0448c02"/>報我言。我飢餓欲取子肉噉之。我<note n="0448054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">問＋（言）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">問＋（言）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448054"><lem>問</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">問言</rdg></app>卿無
<lb n="0448c03"/>有飯可<note n="0448055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食＋（之）【三】</note><note n="0448055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食＋（之）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0448055"><lem>食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">食之</rdg></app>耶。報我言。無有也。我言且待<anchor id="fxT03p0448c01"/>須。
<lb n="0448c04"/>我為汝持飯來。報我言。卿<note n="0448056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔去〕－【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔去〕－【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448056"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>未及出門頃
<lb n="0448c05"/>我便餓死。我心<note n="0448057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">念＋（言）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念＋（言）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448057"><lem>念</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">念言</rdg></app><note n="0448058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">適持兒去＝取兒持去者【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">適持兒去＝取兒持去者【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448058"><lem>適持兒去</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">取兒持去者</rdg></app>。母便當<note n="0448059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（餓）＋死【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（餓）＋死【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448059"><lem>死</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">餓死</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0448c06"/>若捨去者則當取<anchor id="fxT03p0448c02"/>兒<note n="0448060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">噉＋（之）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">噉＋（之）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448060"><lem>噉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">噉之</rdg></app>我便割乳<note n="0448061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便與＝與之【三】，與使【聖】</note><note n="0448061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便與＝與之【宋】【元】【明】，＝與使【聖】</note><app n="0448061"><lem>便與</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">與之</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">與使</rdg></app>噉
<lb n="0448c07"/>之。其男子聞<note n="0448062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＝其【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448062" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之＝其【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448062"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">其</rdg></app>言。即<note n="0448063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00570;＝墮【聖】</note><app n="0448063"><lem>&CB00570;</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">墮</rdg></app>地<note n="0448064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">奄＝掩【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448064" resp="CBETA" type="mod">奄＝掩【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448064"><lem>奄</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">掩</rdg></app>絕。婬<anchor id="fxT03p0448c03"/>女便
<lb n="0448c08"/>取水灑其上。<note n="0448065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">其＝甚【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448065" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其＝甚【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448065"><lem>其</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">甚</rdg></app>久乃得酥息。男子問言。&CB00106;
<lb n="0448c09"/>當為<note n="0448066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">我＝汝【聖】</note><app n="0448066"><lem>我</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">汝</rdg></app>現至誠。婬<anchor id="fxT03p0448c04"/>女言諾。男子言。我初
<lb n="0448c10"/>不見此難。實至誠如汝言不虛者。&CB00106;乳當平
<lb n="0448c11"/>復如故。應時其女人乳平復如故。亦無<note n="0448067" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（瘡）＋瘢【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448067" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（瘡）＋瘢【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448067"><lem>瘢</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">瘡瘢</rdg></app>
<lb n="0448c12"/>也。釋提桓因以天眼<note n="0448068" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＋（之）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448068" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見＋（之）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448068"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">見之</rdg></app><note n="0448069" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婬&CB00105;女＝婬&CB00105;之【宋】，&CB00107;嫉之【元】【明】【聖】</note><note n="0448069" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婬&CB00105;女＝婬&CB00105;之【宋】，＝&CB00107;嫉之【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448069"><lem>婬&CB00105;女</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">婬&CB00105;之</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&CB00107;嫉之</rdg></app>言。此上色
<lb n="0448c13"/>婬女人布施為<note n="0448070" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">福＋（德）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448070" resp="CBETA" type="mod">福＋（德）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448070"><lem>福</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">福德</rdg></app>乃如是。恐來奪我座。<note n="0448071" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">則＝即【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448071" resp="CBETA" type="mod">則＝即【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448071"><lem>則</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">即</rdg></app>
<lb n="0448c14"/>化作婆羅門持<note n="0448072" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寶枝＝三寶杖【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448072" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寶枝＝三寶杖【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448072"><lem>寶枝</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">三寶杖</rdg></app>澡豆瓶。著金錫<note n="0448073" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔杖〕－【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448073" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔杖〕－【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448073"><lem>杖</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0448074" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行乞&CB00456;＝行&CB00456;自【三】，＝空自【聖】</note><note n="0448074" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行乞&CB00456;＝行&CB00456;自【宋】【元】【明】，＝空自【聖】</note><app n="0448074"><lem>行
<lb n="0448c15"/>乞&CB00456;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">行&CB00456;自</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">空自</rdg></app>至<note n="0448075" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＋（上色）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448075" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此＋（上色）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448075"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">此上色</rdg></app>婬女家言。<note n="0448076" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乞＝與【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448076" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乞＝與【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448076"><lem>乞</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">與</rdg></app>我分衛。其女人
<lb n="0448c16"/>便以金&CB00425;盛飯出與婆羅門。婆羅門即&CB00230;<note n="0448077" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔行〕－【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448077" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔行〕－【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448077"><lem>行</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0448c17"/>不肯受。上色<anchor id="fxT03p0448c05"/>女問<note n="0448078" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道人＝婆羅門言【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448078" resp="CBETA" type="mod">道人＝婆羅門言【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448078"><lem>道人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">婆羅門言</rdg></app>。何為&CB00230;行不肯受
<lb n="0448c18"/>食。報言。我不用食。我聞汝布施乳為審爾
<lb n="0448c19"/>不乎。報言。實如是。婆羅門以偈問<note n="0448079" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448079" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔之〕－【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448079"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>曰</p>
<lb n="0448c20"/><lg><l>汝為索何<note n="0448080" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">願＋（事）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448080" resp="CBETA" type="mod">願＋（事）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448080"><lem>願</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">願事</rdg></app></l><l>云何釋為<note n="0448081" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">梵＋（耶）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0448081" resp="CBETA" type="mod">梵＋（耶）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0448081"><lem>梵</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">梵耶</rdg></app></l>
<pb ed="T" id="T03.0178.0449a" n="0449a"/>
<lb n="0449a01"/><l><note n="0449001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（若）＋為【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（若）＋為【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449001"><lem>為</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">若為</rdg></app>求多寶<note n="0449002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＝玉【三】</note><note n="0449002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王＝玉【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0449002"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">玉</rdg></app></l><l>所願難<note n="0449003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（乃）＋如【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（乃）＋如【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449003"><lem>如</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">乃如</rdg></app>是</l></lg>
<lb n="0449a02"/><p>上色<anchor id="fxT03p0449a01"/>女。以偈報之言</p>
<lb n="0449a03"/><lg><l><note n="0449004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婆羅門＝所可作【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婆羅門＝所可作【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449004"><lem>婆羅門</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">所可作</rdg></app>無為者</l><l>無生老及病死</l>
<lb n="0449a04"/><l>無<note n="0449005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">愁憂＝憂愁【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">愁憂＝憂愁【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449005"><lem>愁憂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">憂愁</rdg></app>清淨處</l><l>婆羅門我求彼</l></lg>
<lb n="0449a05"/><p>婆羅門<note n="0449006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言問＝問言【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言問＝問言【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449006"><lem>言。問</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">問言</rdg></app>汝持乳布施時。意寧轉異不。
<lb n="0449a06"/>女人報言。婆羅門。我當為汝現至誠。報言
<lb n="0449a07"/>現之。女人言。若使我至誠持乳布施意<note n="0449007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無＋（有）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無＋（有）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449007"><lem>無</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">無有</rdg></app>
<lb n="0449a08"/>異者。令我轉女人身得作男子。所言<note n="0449008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">適竟＝這意【聖】</note><app n="0449008"><lem>適竟</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">這意</rdg></app>
<lb n="0449a09"/>即轉成男子。時優波羅越王治國五千歲已
<lb n="0449a10"/>後終亡。傍臣左右聞婬女人轉身作男子。念
<lb n="0449a11"/>言正當立此作國王。為王者當以正法治國。
<lb n="0449a12"/>便共立作王。鞭杖不行以<note n="0449009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">正法＝王法【元】，〔正〕－【聖】</note><app n="0449009"><lem>正法</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">王法</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">法</rdg></app>治國。好布施
<lb n="0449a13"/>金銀珍寶著四城門<note n="0449010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔外〕－【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔外〕－【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449010"><lem>外</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>及諸街里。欲得<note n="0449011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（飯食…舍宅）十四字＝（飯者與飯欲得財者與財欲得衣者與衣欲得香熏花者與熏華欲得房室坐席者與房室坐席欲得舍宅者與舍宅欲得）四十八字【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（飯食…舍宅）十四字＝（飯者與飯欲得財者與財欲得衣者與衣欲得香熏花者與熏華欲得房室坐席者與房室坐席欲得舍宅者與舍宅欲得）四十八字【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449011" word-count="14"><lem>飯
<lb n="0449a14"/>食漿水衣被熏華房室座席舍宅</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">飯者與飯欲得財者與財欲得衣者與衣欲得香熏花者與熏華欲得房室坐席者與房室坐席欲得舍宅者與舍宅欲得</rdg></app>金銀珍寶明
<lb n="0449a15"/>月珠玉琉璃水精珊瑚馬瑙。隨<note n="0449012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">其＝所【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其＝所【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449012"><lem>其</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">所</rdg></app>欲與之。
<lb n="0449a16"/><note n="0449013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一〕－【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449013"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>教天下人持八關齋。如是治國五百歲。不
<lb n="0449a17"/>耕種自然<note n="0449014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（生）＋稻【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（生）＋稻【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449014"><lem>稻</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">生稻</rdg></app>米清潔香美無有&CB00308;獷。今日截
<lb n="0449a18"/>旦<note n="0449015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔日〕－【三】【明】</note><note n="0449015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔日〕－【宋】【元】【明】【明】</note><app n="0449015"><lem>日</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>續自然生。即取<note n="0449016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔其〕－【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔其〕－【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449016"><lem>其</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>米莖應時沒不現。
<lb n="0449a19"/>取共食<note n="0449017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（其）＋味【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（其）＋味【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449017"><lem>味</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">其味</rdg></app>。一切味食是<note n="0449018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝以【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已＝以【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449018"><lem>已</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app>後齒不落。亦不
<lb n="0449a20"/>老亦不病。亦不傴。顏色無異長短適等。祿
<lb n="0449a21"/>相亦等。譬如&CB00614;單<note n="0449019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">越＝曰【聖】</note><app n="0449019"><lem>越</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">曰</rdg></app>天<note n="0449020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">下＋（人）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">下＋（人）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449020"><lem>下</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">下人</rdg></app>。國王自念言。
<lb n="0449a22"/>我布施與人<note n="0449021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔有〕－【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔有〕－【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449021"><lem>有</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>何可怪。<note n="0449022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">我＝哉【聖】</note><app n="0449022"><lem>我</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">哉</rdg></app>布施與禽獸者
<lb n="0449a23"/>爾乃為難。時王<note n="0449023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（以）＋穌【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（以）＋穌【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449023"><lem>穌</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">以穌</rdg></app>香自塗身。便入山空閑
<lb n="0449a24"/>處臥巖石上。諸百鳥皆來生瞰其身。便命過
<lb n="0449a25"/>生於婆羅門家。其家大富金銀珍寶無央數。
<lb n="0449a26"/>十月已滿便生端正好無比。<anchor id="fxT03p0449a02"/>適生四侍女共
<lb n="0449a27"/>養育。第一女主<note n="0449024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拭＝莊飾【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拭＝莊飾【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449024"><lem>拭</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">莊飾</rdg></app>其身。第二女主沐浴。第
<lb n="0449a28"/>三女主乳哺。第四女主抱之。兒即長大四<note n="0449025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（大）＋人【宋】，（夫）＋人【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449025"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">大人</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">夫人</rdg></app>
<lb n="0449a29"/>共侍<note n="0449026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">議＝護【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">議＝護【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449026"><lem>議</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">護</rdg></app>。不得使有見者。五<note n="0449027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔百〕－【聖】</note><app n="0449027"><lem>百</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>綵女共侍相
<pb ed="T" id="T03.0178.0449b" n="0449b"/>
<lb n="0449b01"/>娛樂。便竊出過向市。觀見販賣貧窮乞&CB00456;者。
<lb n="0449b02"/>有悲哀之意言。此人民若使富樂者。不復賈
<lb n="0449b03"/>作販賣。爾時自說偈言</p>
<lb n="0449b04"/><lg><l>我之身心云何</l><l><note n="0449028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甚＝其【三】</note><note n="0449028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">甚＝其【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0449028"><lem>甚</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">其</rdg></app>堅而<note n="0449029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＝石【聖】</note><app n="0449029"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">石</rdg></app>破碎</l>
<lb n="0449b05"/><l>吾自在安樂處</l><l>見勤苦諸人民</l></lg>
<lb n="0449b06"/><p><note n="0449030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">馳＝便【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">馳＝便【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449030"><lem>馳</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">便</rdg></app>還白父母。我欲除鬚髮行入山<note n="0449031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">空處處＝於空閑【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">空處處＝於空閑【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449031"><lem>空處處</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">於空閑</rdg></app>
<lb n="0449b07"/>樹下。父母不聽。所以者何。<anchor id="fxT03p0449b01"/>適有汝一子甚
<lb n="0449b08"/><note n="0449032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">重愛＝愛重【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">重愛＝愛重【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449032"><lem>重愛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">愛重</rdg></app>之。我禱祠山川日月諸天。<anchor id="fxT03p0449b02"/>適得汝一
<lb n="0449b09"/>子耳。我不見汝者便愁憂死。不肯聽使去。
<lb n="0449b10"/>子便委臥地一日二日至五日不食飲。諸親
<lb n="0449b11"/>厚知識聞此兒欲學道除鬚髮。父母不聽。委
<lb n="0449b12"/>臥空地不<note n="0449033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食飲＝飲食【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食飲＝飲食【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449033"><lem>食飲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">飲食</rdg></app>五日。諸親厚知識皆共到其
<lb n="0449b13"/>所諫曉言。童子。何以不起沐浴飲食莊嚴<note n="0449034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道＋（為）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449034" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><corr sic="道" resp="Maha">用</corr>＋（為）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449034"><lem>用</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">用為</rdg></app>
<lb n="0449b14"/>除鬚髮在樹間樂<note n="0449035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道＋（乎）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">道＋（乎）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449035"><lem>道</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">道乎</rdg></app>。童子亦不應。如是言
<lb n="0449b15"/><note n="0449036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">者＝至【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者＝至【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449036"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">至</rdg></app>三<note n="0449037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">日＝反【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">日＝反【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449037"><lem>日</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">反</rdg></app>。諸親厚共到父母所言。聽使去學
<lb n="0449b16"/>道。若樂者可數<note n="0449038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">來往＝往來【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">來往＝往來【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449038"><lem>來往</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">往來</rdg></app>相見。不樂者便當來
<lb n="0449b17"/>歸。父母言<note n="0449039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諾＋（子）【三】，＝諸子【聖】</note><note n="0449039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諾＋（子）【宋】【元】【明】，＝諸子【聖】</note><app n="0449039"><lem>諾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">諾子</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">諸子</rdg></app>。見聽已<note n="0449040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔子〕－【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔子〕－【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449040"><lem>子</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>便自養視。六七
<lb n="0449b18"/>日繞父母三匝為作禮。便<note n="0449041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入＋（山）【聖】</note><app n="0449041"><lem>入</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">入山</rdg></app><note n="0449042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">空閑＝空樹下【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">空閑＝空樹下【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449042"><lem>空閑</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">空樹下</rdg></app>坐行道
<lb n="0449b19"/>已後。則往至餘大叢樹間。中有兩道人坐得
<lb n="0449b20"/>五神通。精誠求道<note n="0449043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">離＋（於）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">離＋（於）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449043"><lem>離</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">離於</rdg></app>婬欲。童子便至其所
<lb n="0449b21"/>問。此間作何等。報言。我在此間露坐禪念
<lb n="0449b22"/>道。用人民故作勤苦行。童子言。我亦當用人
<lb n="0449b23"/>民故露坐禪念道。二道人言。善童子。即於大
<lb n="0449b24"/>叢樹下坐禪。於<note n="0449044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（其）＋中【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（其）＋中【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449044"><lem>中</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">其中</rdg></app>用人民故勤苦行道。即得
<lb n="0449b25"/>五神通。精進踰於<note n="0449045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝兩【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二＝兩【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449045"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">兩</rdg></app>道人。其人<note n="0449046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＋（神）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大＋（神）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449046"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">大神</rdg></app>聖上尊。
<lb n="0449b26"/>其樹間有虎<note n="0449047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妊娠＝妊身【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妊娠＝妊身【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449047"><lem>妊娠</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">妊身</rdg></app>。諸道人法樹<note n="0449048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">果＝&CB00031;【宋】【元】【聖】</note><app n="0449048"><lem>果</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&CB00031;</rdg></app>自墮落
<lb n="0449b27"/>者乃取食之。不從樹摘取也。諸道人共行求
<lb n="0449b28"/><anchor id="fxT03p0449b03"/>果蓏。便見<anchor id="fxT03p0449b04"/>妊娠虎。童子道人<note n="0449049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">語＝詣【聖】</note><app n="0449049"><lem>語</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">詣</rdg></app>兩道人
<lb n="0449b29"/>言。此虎今不久當<note n="0449050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">產＝生【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">產＝生【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449050"><lem>產</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">生</rdg></app>。飢餓經日恐自噉其
<pb ed="T" id="T03.0178.0449c" n="0449c"/>
<lb n="0449c01"/>子。誰能持身<note n="0449051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食＝餧【三】【聖】＊</note><note n="0449051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食＝餧【宋】【元】【明】【聖】＊</note><app n="0449051"><lem>食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">餧</rdg></app>之者。彌勒菩薩言。我當持
<lb n="0449c02"/>身<anchor id="fxT03p0449c01"/>食之。採<anchor id="fxT03p0449c02"/>果還已見<note n="0449052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">虎＋（已）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">虎＋（已）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449052"><lem>虎</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">虎已</rdg></app>乳飢餓欲取其
<lb n="0449c03"/>子<note n="0449053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔噉之〕－【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔噉之〕－【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449053"><lem>噉之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。其<note n="0449054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（一）＋道人【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（一）＋道人【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449054"><lem>道人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">一道人</rdg></app>語兩道人言。虎已乳飢餓
<lb n="0449c04"/>欲還<note n="0449055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">噉＝取【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">噉＝取【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449055"><lem>噉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">取</rdg></app>其<note n="0449056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">子＋（食之）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">子＋（食之）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449056"><lem>子</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">子食之</rdg></app>。誰能持身<note n="0449057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食之＝飼者彌勒菩薩言我當持身飼之【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食之＝飼者彌勒菩薩言我當持身飼之【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449057"><lem>食之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">飼者彌勒菩薩言我當持身飼之</rdg></app>。便共俱至餓
<lb n="0449c05"/>虎所。虎<note n="0449058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">開目＝因【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">開目＝因【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449058"><lem>開目</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">因</rdg></app>張口向之。兩道人俱畏懼。便
<lb n="0449c06"/>飛上虛空中。其一<note n="0449059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（道）＋人【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（道）＋人【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449059"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">道人</rdg></app>言。<note n="0449060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道人＝云何【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">道人＝云何【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449060"><lem>道人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">云何</rdg></app>卿之至誠如
<lb n="0449c07"/>是<note n="0449061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">也＝耶【三】【聖】＊</note><note n="0449061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">也＝耶【宋】【元】【明】【聖】＊</note><app n="0449061"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">耶</rdg></app>。屬者言。當持身<note n="0449062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食＝飼【三】【聖】＊</note><note n="0449062" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食＝飼【宋】【元】【明】【聖】＊</note><app n="0449062"><lem>食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">飼</rdg></app>餓虎。今者何故
<lb n="0449c08"/>飛上虛空<anchor id="fxT03p0449c03"/>也其一道人哀之淚出。左右顧
<lb n="0449c09"/><note n="0449063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔視〕－【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449063" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔視〕－【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449063"><lem>視</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>無所有。童子道人取利刀刺右臂<note n="0449064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（放）＋流【三】</note><note n="0449064" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（放）＋流【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0449064"><lem>流</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">放流</rdg></app>血。
<lb n="0449c10"/>如是七處自刺。<note n="0449065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（放）＋血【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449065" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（放）＋血【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449065"><lem>血</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">放血</rdg></app>入虎口中<note n="0449066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（虎）＋因【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449066" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（虎）＋因【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449066"><lem>因</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">虎因</rdg></app>飲之。便復
<lb n="0449c11"/>自投身<anchor id="fxT03p0449c04"/>食餓虎<note n="0449067" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">則＝童子道人即【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449067" resp="CBETA" type="mod">則＝童子道人即【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449067"><lem>則</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">童子道人即</rdg></app>死。佛語阿難。欲知爾時
<lb n="0449c12"/>上色婬女人者不。正是我身。時立為王者。
<lb n="0449c13"/>亦是我身。時婆羅門子自投身<note n="0449068" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">餧＝飼【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449068" resp="CBETA" type="mod">餧＝飼【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449068"><lem>餧</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">飼</rdg></app>餓虎者。
<lb n="0449c14"/>亦是我身。兩道人者。是迦<note n="0449069" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">葉＋（菩薩）【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449069" resp="CBETA" type="mod">葉＋（菩薩）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449069"><lem>葉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">葉菩薩</rdg></app>彌勒菩薩。佛
<lb n="0449c15"/>告阿難。我精進行<note n="0449070" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔道〕－【聖】</note><app n="0449070"><lem>道</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>故。超越九劫出<note n="0449071" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">彌勒＋（菩薩）【三】</note><note n="0449071" resp="CBETA" type="mod">彌勒＋（菩薩）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0449071"><lem>彌勒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">彌勒菩薩</rdg></app>
<lb n="0449c16"/>前。如是阿難。勤苦行道六十劫。布施手足
<lb n="0449c17"/>鼻耳頭目肌肉婦子男女好衣被飲食故。降
<lb n="0449c18"/>伏六十億魔。三十四億得佛道。佛語阿難若
<lb n="0449c19"/>使一切人知布施之福如我所知者。窮乏餬
<lb n="0449c20"/>口得一食自飯繼命。若不食此便<note n="0449072" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（餓）＋死【三】【聖】</note><note n="0449072" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（餓）＋死【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0449072"><lem>死</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">餓死</rdg></app>者。則
<pb ed="T" id="T03.0178.0450a" n="0450a"/>
<lb n="0450a01"/>當不自食與善人令受。阿難。我念昔世時所
<lb n="0450a02"/>布施。用是故面色明好照曜。笑光從口出遍
<lb n="0450a03"/>三千大千世界。佛說是經時。四千二百比丘
<lb n="0450a04"/>起無餘意得解脫。八十那術諸天人發無上
<lb n="0450a05"/>正真道意。七萬菩薩得無所從生法忍。佛說
<lb n="0450a06"/>如是。賢者阿難及一切眾會諸天龍鬼神世
<lb n="0450a07"/>間人皆歡喜。前為佛作禮而去</p>
